description.en:
BitTorro is a crypto to crypto, wallet to wallet, no-custody, swap exchange service. Here you can instant swap one cryptocurrency for another in minutes. As a privacy focused platform, your personal data are safe and never shared.

But, BitTorro is not only that. We have a mission and that’s to create a sustainable way to support non ICO, open-source, decentralised blockchain development. When you buy your favourite crypto, you’re also supporting the blockchain development of your project because we will donate a portion of swap revenue.
